  "body": "Currently, `request_mirror_policy` [0] only supports to config modes:\r\n\r\na) `runtime_key` not set, so 100% of requests get mirrored\r\nb) `runtime_key` is set, so it relies on the runtime key to determine the percentage of traffic\r\n\r\nWe have a need for a third mode which is:\r\n\r\nc) allow setting the percentage via a config key (e.g.: `default_percentage`)\r\n\r\nDoes this sound reasonable? If so, I'll send a PR.\r\n\r\n[0] https://github.com/envoyproxy/envoy/blob/master/api/envoy/api/v2/route/route.proto#L622",
